commit.title: Fixes according to feedback
commit.message:
Fixes according to feedback

- deprecated  tactics in PreOmega.v
  omega with * is now implemented by zify ; omega
- removed dependency to Program
- use EConstr.Unsafe.to_constr for keys in hash tables and maps
Co-Authored-By: Gaëtan Gilbert <gaetan.gilbert@skyskimmer.net>
- dead code removal and zify.mli
- fix efficiency bug in lia (optimised cnf)
